%package doc
Summary:        C++ implementation header files for JMS-like messaging
Group:          Documentation for the CMS API
%if %{?fedora}%{!?fedora:0} >= 10 || %{?rhel}%{!?rhel:0} >= 6
BuildArch:      noarch
%endif

%description doc
